Summary: UFO spotted in Horsham, PA on April 12, 2012 at 20:00 hours
divs: Sighting DetailsI observed a disc-shaped object which appeared over my neighbor's house in back of me. It was fairly low in the sky and it stopped moving and then totally disappeared. The object was glowing and was a neon green color with white lights on it. It was approximately 8:00 p.m. I did not spot any further sightings that evening.
